                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;'>In Singapore, there are several debt consolidation options available to individuals looking to streamline their debts and manage their repayments more effectively.&nbsp;</p>
